    -m "feat: off-hardware ASE verification — fail-closed attestation suite, KRS policy enforcement (rate-limit §1.4) + tests, PQC-TLS live hybrid handshake on OpenSSL 3.5 (X25519MLKEM768)" \
    -m "Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>"
